Field Description: Current status of the corresponding reference
First author name + et al. + publication date of reference
DOI or PMID for the reference
Specific host involved (i.e. dairy cows, beef calves)
Stage of production relevant to study intervention
Set of result fields available in the study (i.e. Contingency Table, Rate Table)
Contingency Table: # AMR+ in exposed group
Contingency Table: # AMR- in exposed group
Contingency Table: # AMR+ in referent group
Contingency Table: # AMR- in referent group
Rate Table: % AMR+ in exposed group
Rate Table: % AMR+ in referent group
Odds Ratio: Odds ratio value for the factor
When TRUE, factor is to be excluded from the iAM.AMR models
Meta-analysis type (i.e. within studies, across studies) (if applicable)
